HEADWORD: Polyarchy
<hw>Pol"y*ar`chy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Poly-</ets>
+ <ets>-archy</ets>: cf. F. <ets>polyarchie.</ets> Cf.
<er>Polarchy</er>.]</ety> <def>A government by many persons, of whatever
order or class.</def> <rj><au>Cudworth.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
